### CRM Clients API (Admin)

### List all clients
GET {{baseUrl}}/clients
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Search by phone prefix
GET {{baseUrl}}/clients/search?phone=1956
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### List reschedule credits by phone (staff/admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/clients/credits?phone=+19566161714&phoneCountry=US
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Update client (by normalized phone key)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/clients/19561231234
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Name",
  "phone": "+19561231234"
}

###

### Delete client
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/clients/19561231234
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
